organic.title: Human Services | Wadena County, MN - Official Website
organic.snippet: The Wadena County Human Services Department includes social services, financial and medical services, and more.

organic.title: Child Protection | Wadena County, MN - Official Website
organic.snippet: Child Protection reports can be made 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. The intake social worker is available from 8:00 am – 4:30 pm Monday-Friday.

organic.title: Home and Community Based Services | Wadena County, MN
organic.snippet: We can help seniors apply for public assistance and navigate through home and community-based Medicaid programs, home care services and specialized housing.

organic.title: Family and Health Services | Wadena County, MN - Official Website
organic.snippet: provides a broad range of services to individuals, families, and communities to promote and protect the health of those who live and work in Wadena County.
